{"tid":1427389,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文] 唔割蓆唔代表你應該做","createTime":"2019-08-07T06:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:34:49.000Z","uid":184163,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"516288f279f134cf01f0a942100d0d421b37ed8e","tid":1427389,"uid":184163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:01:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無論做咩都唔割蓆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係講緊事後，當同路人動咗手之後，我哋應該有嘅態度。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但絕對唔代表你做得啱</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最近有好多手足，係做一啲可能會引起爭議嘅決定嗰時，都會開po問，咁做嘅話會唔會有人割蓆。<br />\n<br />\n其實係搞錯咗個問題。<br />\n<br />\n你應該問嘅係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">贊唔贊成咁樣做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而當大部份同路大都唔贊成咁做，<br />\n你就唔應該做。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「不割蓆」不應該成為行動嘅理據。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n需要明白嘅係，我哋其實已經係命運共同體。只要我哋曾經發過同一場夢，係敵人眼中我哋自然係一夥。<br />\n<br />\n而當有手足做咗大部份人唔贊成嘅舉動，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除咗有機俾敵人借題發揮，亦都影響內部士氣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;講咗唔好咁做㗎啦&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;唔明點解要咁做&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;又俾位人入&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n類似嘅言論，大家都見唔少。<br />\n一有呢啲言論，大家好自然會歸邊，然後爭論。<br />\n<br />\n一爭論，重要嘅post會沉底之餘，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">亦會將原本一致對外嘅槍頭轉為對內</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n經過幾個循環，整個運動就好容易被瓦解。<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋要時刻保持理性思考，老套啲講句，要顧全大局。<br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落，唔好一齊輸，要一齊贏！"},{"pid":"747ef77eb9ef5deabe21840181e66d75546fb125","tid":1427389,"uid":184163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<br />\n我冇嘢講！"},{"pid":"d5b05bd332855a4098f5c94ae6535c6e3b583e1d","tid":1427389,"uid":184163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:02:30.000Z","msg":"我要見律師"},{"pid":"cc2c3459a2b1586e63d5cc5382eec145a32e161b","tid":1427389,"uid":184163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:02:44.000Z","msg":"我要去醫院驗傷"},{"pid":"b5ccc7a83add8ee829f35e1facb04d6aa6be76cf","tid":1427389,"uid":184163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:02:54.000Z","msg":"唔好兇我"},{"pid":"e2f3d7894dae069d9ca933a10e11c14a9ba3f4fc","tid":1427389,"uid":184163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:03:04.000Z","msg":"我要投訴你"},{"pid":"f39d8b3e9bf4dced6fb8c9148b8c384f4122c229","tid":1427389,"uid":204356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:03:05.000Z","msg":"Agree <br />\nPush<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cd2f53294d51eb95c2afde9f8b007771652de1","tid":1427389,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:03:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c5188900fc61e9fbf6a9b2298f9cc820f7c0ef7","tid":1427389,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:03:15.000Z","msg":"我要飲食"},{"pid":"f3d47a55fe874f07b31dc8c0138fe2ad238e45c1","tid":1427389,"uid":184163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:03:47.000Z","msg":"再推<br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落"},{"pid":"3644a1ca400533422c5681452361df4f14739ac2","tid":1427389,"uid":184163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:04:03.000Z","msg":"Be water"},{"pid":"a2087e24e24072c1605731fbb8a5f21445f13c07","tid":1427389,"uid":3318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:04:39.000Z","msg":"G持 保持冷靜頭腦 獨立思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74adce7f80f077058da980fb3c8e84caf0a37a92","tid":1427389,"uid":184163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:04:59.000Z","msg":"不要被仇恨沖昏頭腦"},{"pid":"58bf971b057b2e2d742fa7901cf8dfbd1df2df95","tid":1427389,"uid":184163,"like"